{"title":"街头诗四首","authors":["红杨树"],"dates":[{"year":1950,"month":12,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"街头诗四首"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红杨树"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要忘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当成吨的烧夷弹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在朝鲜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞腾起无边大火的时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同志们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要忘记——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝鲜人和你蹲在一个战壕里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃苦菜的那些日子。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当一只得寸进尺的野兽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向你扑来的时候，朋友们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有它自己的血"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才能够教训他自己。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一颗美国子弹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到今天，还包在我的血肉里呀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要带着它，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到鸭绿江的那岸去。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回答"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲爱的志愿军"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要打，就要狠！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请用俘掳数字"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回答麦克阿瑟的野心。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}